{"tid":2461742,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"一人一信 投訴李百全","createTime":"2021-03-25T14:07:16.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-25T15:17:17.000Z","uid":277218,"like":12,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"eea55e7f60df67f7d4e145129abecc7666c8f01d","tid":2461742,"uid":277218,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-25T14:07:16.000Z","msg":"致申訴專員公署complaints@ombudsman.hk <br />\n副本： ccu@rthk.hk, ccibenq@cedb.gov.hk<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;<br />\n<br />\n致：申訴專員公署<br />\n副本：香港電台、商務及經濟發展局<br />\n<br />\n主題：不滿及投訴廣播處長李百全行政失當<br />\n<br />\n本人是一名香港市民，亦是香港電台的忠實觀眾，近日因香港電台的節目頻繁調動，對我使用該公營機構服務時大受影響，特來信申訴。<br />\n<br />\n香港電台本來在 2021 年 3 月 11 日 20:00 播放《議事論事》，在當晚七點多才忽然抽起，事前毫無通知，嚴重影響觀眾的預期。另外原定於 2021 年 3 月 12 日 19:10 播放《The Pulse》 ，20:00 播放《鏗鏘說》，但兩個節目忽然對調，卻要等到 19:12 才在電視上宣佈對調。<br />\n <br />\n《電視通用業務守則 &mdash; 節目標準》第 12 章 11 節規定電視台若要調動節目，應採取合理措施去通知觀眾，香港電台在節目對調後才通知觀眾，明顯違反了相關規定。<br />\n<br />\n而另一節目《香港故事》本來有一個周冠威的專題，該專題早已在媒體上宣傳，最終卻無緣無故被抽起，相關決定由廣播處長李百全及助理廣播處長區麗雅作出。《香港電台約章》列明，香港電台應享有編輯自主，李百全及區麗雅干涉編輯自主，行政失當，濫用職權，除了違反《香港電台約章》，亦令我等觀眾極度失望，請申訴專員立案調查。<br />\n<br />\n另外，最新得知《鏗鏘說》節目即將換上立場偏建制的主持，這也是破壞港台一向中立的形象，實在令觀眾感到遺憾！<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n香港電台電視部忠實觀眾<br />\nXXX 謹啟<br />\n日期<br />\n<br />\n&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;<br />\n<br />\n🚥 希望大家都可以幫手改少少內文，效果更好！"},{"pid":"ef76ce75c3347b04adb1a98823c5996f575233c1","tid":2461742,"uid":146285,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-25T14:32:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d752923d8cde5bc6ec534bc3175f0ab65b0d9f2a","tid":2461742,"uid":146285,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-25T14:32:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e6238301650cdaed65c28351b0a3f8d04f50c834","tid":2461742,"uid":84176,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-25T14:36:03.000Z","msg":"寫定投訴埋香港申訴專員公署都得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2cdd9d004b41b22e6a65efd043fab6eb005349e0","tid":2461742,"uid":277640,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-25T14:39:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6c1d1bdfa836984e8e5edf5a1a8a634521944092","tid":2461742,"uid":277640,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-25T14:40:01.000Z","msg":"正經事，推"},{"pid":"580e8bbac05d221c2d2c94177093c2ae543b3417","tid":2461742,"uid":292292,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-25T14:42:48.000Z","msg":"當你知道申訴專員公署老闆係邊個果陣, 仲會投訴嗎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f99494b149cc8d4bd22820543db0a434c4128af8","tid":2461742,"uid":66546,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-25T14:51:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c1830818afc0921584e634f82758fc7dd824a472","tid":2461742,"uid":53498,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-25T15:01:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3792475ad8a78a93fd92613a82a4f96299852874","tid":2461742,"uid":54681,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-25T15:02:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"95188d20b7728ea395bf4f0d230f2f3783f66d61","tid":2461742,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-25T15:02:52.000Z","msg":"<im